#ROOM
Vnum     36550
Name     &xWestern Gate from the Badlands&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The orange dust of the Badlands is suddenly cut short by a jagged, 
black-rock ravine. The air is thick with the scent of sulfur and 
burning coal. A massive iron gate, built by the Dark Iron dwarves, 
stands open, leading into the smoke-choked sky of the Searing Gorge.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    35522
Desc      Return to the Badlands ridge path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36551
Desc      The road leads into the Gorge.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36516 5 36550
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36551
Name     &xThe Slag Road&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A wide, soot-covered trail leads between towering cliffs of 
volcanic rock. To the north, the ground falls away into a 
massive basin filled with smoldering slag heaps and the 
skeletons of giant machines.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36550
Desc      The western gate.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36552
Desc      The road continues toward the mountain.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36565
Desc      The descent into the Slag Pit.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36501 5 36551
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36552
Name     &xThe Ashlands&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The ground here is covered in a deep layer of grey ash. Strange, 
jagged obsidian formations rise from the plains like the 
claws of some buried monster. The heat is intense, and the 
sky is a permanent, bruised purple.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36551
Desc      The slag road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36553
Desc      The approach to the Great Bridge.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36500 5 36552
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36553
Name     &xApproach to the Blackrock Bridge&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The road narrows as it leads toward a massive iron bridge that 
spans a wide, lava-filled canyon. To the west, the base of 
Blackrock Mountain towers over the land, its peaks lost in 
the smoke.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36552
Desc      The ashlands.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36554
Desc      Cross the Iron Bridge.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36513 5 36553
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36554
Name     &rThe Great Blackrock Bridge&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A triumph of Dark Iron engineering, this bridge is made of 
solid black iron and anchored deep into the living rock. 
Far below, a river of magma flows north, lighting the 
canyon walls in a hellish orange glow.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36553
Desc      Return to the approach.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36555
Desc      The mountain entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36509 1 36554
  Reset G 1 36551 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36555
Name     &rGate of Blackrock Mountain&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand at the massive base of the mountain. A series of 
wide, iron-shod stairs leads up into the dark, while the 
air rumbles with the sound of thousands of hammers and 
the heartbeat of the earth itself.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36554
Desc      The great bridge.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36556
Desc      Enter the Hall of the Mountain.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36519 5 36555
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36556
Name     &rThe Hall of the Mountain&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A cavernous entry hall built to accommodate the massive 
machinery of the Dark Irons. To the north and south, 
balconies overlook the deep pits of the mountain, while 
central stairs lead deeper into the stone.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36555
Desc      The mountain gate.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36561
Desc      The Spire Landing (Portal Hub).~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36560
Desc      The Depths Entrance (Portal Hub).~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36562
Desc      The Window of the Core (Portal Hub).~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36522 5 36556
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36560
Name     &rEntrance to the Blackrock Depths&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide, descending ramp leads toward the lower city of the 
Dark Irons. This is the gateway to the Blackrock Depths, 
a sprawling metropolis of iron, fire, and industry. A 
heavy iron gate glows with the heat of the city below.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36556
Desc      The mountain hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36561
Name     &rThe Spire Landing&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone landing that overlooks the upper reaches of 
Blackrock Mountain. Stone stairs wind upward toward the 
entrance of Blackrock Spire, where the black dragonflight 
makes its nest in the high peaks.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36556
Desc      The mountain hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36562
Name     &rThe Window of the Core&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A narrow ledge overlooking a massive, vertical shaft that 
leads straight down into the molten heart of the mountain. 
A shimmering, white-hot portal marks the entrance to the 
Molten Core, the domain of the Firelord.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36556
Desc      The mountain hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36563
Name     &rThe Blackwing Lair Overlook&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high, secluded balcony reached through the upper spire. 
From here, the entrance to Nefarian's sanctum—the Blackwing 
Lair—is visible through a shimmering orb of draconic energy.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    36561
Desc      Return to the landing.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36564
Name     &xThorium Point - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A small, well-defended outpost built into the northern ridge 
of the Gorge. The members of the Thorium Brotherhood work 
here in peace, separated from their fanatical kin.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36552
Desc      The ashlands.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36565
Desc      The main square of Thorium Point.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36508 5 36564
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36565
Name     &xThorium Point - Plaza&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     The center of the Brotherhood outpost. Several large anvils 
stand in the open air, and the sound of hammering is 
constant. A small, soot-stained inn provides shelter 
for travelers and smiths alike.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36564
Desc      The southern entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36566
Desc      The Brotherhood Inn.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36567
Desc      The Flight Path.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36518 1 36565
Reset O 0 36549 5 36565
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36566
Name     &xThe Thorium Anvil&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A warm, smoky inn that smells of charcoal and dark ale. 
The walls are decorated with masterfully crafted weapons 
and pieces of thorium armor.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36565
Desc      The plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36567
Name     &xThorium Point - Flight Roost&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A flat, stone ledge overlooking the northern Gorge. Several 
gryphons and wyverns rest here, ready to carry messages 
and cargo out of the smoke.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36565
Desc      The plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36568
Name     &xThe Slag Pit - Descent&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A series of rickety wooden ramps and ladders leads down into 
the massive, bowl-shaped basin known as the Slag Pit. 
The air is thick with the smoke from hundreds of forges.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36551
Desc      The slag road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The bottom of the Slag Pit.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36500 5 36568
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36569
Name     &xThe Slag Pit - Basin&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The bottom of the Gorge's industrial heart. Slaves work 
tirelessly in the heat, while Dark Iron taskmasters 
patrol with whips and hammers. Piles of glowing slag 
are stacked everywhere.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    36568
Desc      Return to the surface.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36570
Desc      The Iron Summit.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36574
Desc      The Firegut Caves.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36521 10 36569
Reset O 0 36533 10 36569
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36570
Name     &xThe Iron Summit&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A high stone platform in the center of the Slag Pit where the 
Dark Iron engineers oversee the work. A massive steam 
engine chugs rhythmically, powering the various elevators.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The basin floor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36571
Desc      The Overseer's Office.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36510 5 36570
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36571
Name     &xThe Overseer's Office&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small, well-furnished stone building overlooking the pit. 
Maps of the mountain's tunnels and production quotas 
are pinned to the walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36570
Desc      The summit.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36500 5 36571
Reset O 0 36543 5 36571
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36572
Name     &xSlave Quarters&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A series of cramped, dirty tunnels where the slaves are 
housed. The air is stagnant and filled with the scent 
of hopelessness and sickness.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The basin floor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36521 10 36572
Reset O 0 36539 1 36572
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36573
Name     &xThe Slag Heap&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A massive pile of burning waste from the forges. Scorpions 
prowl through the glowing embers, feeding on the small 
fire elementals that spawn here.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The basin floor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36504 5 36573
Reset O 0 36528 10 36573
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36574
Name     &yFiregut Caves - Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The natural caverns on the eastern side of the Slag Pit are 
controlled by the Firegut ogres. The walls are decorated 
with crude, bloody drawings and piles of animal bones.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The basin floor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36575
Desc      The main ogre cavern.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36505 5 36574
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36575
Name     &yFiregut Caves - Main Hall&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive natural chamber lit by several large bonfires. 
Firegut ogres rest on piles of furs, while others 
sharpen their crude wooden clubs.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36574
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36576
Desc      The Mystic's Alcove.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36515 5 36575
Reset O 0 36529 5 36575
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36576
Name     &yThe Mystic's Alcove&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air is thick with the scent of burning herbs. A Firegut 
shaman kneels before a large obsidian skull, muttering 
incantations that cause the flames to dance.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36575
Desc      The main hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36512 1 36576
  Reset G 1 36547 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36577
Name     &xThe Obsidian Cliffs&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A high, jagged ridge of volcanic glass overlooking the 
western Gorge. The cliff face is nearly vertical, and 
small lava-spiders crawl along its surface.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36552
Desc      The ashlands.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36524 10 36577
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36578
Name     &xThe Magma Fissure&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The earth has split open here, revealing a deep, glowing 
river of magma below. Intense heat radiates from the 
crack, and the air hums with elemental energy.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36551
Desc      The slag road.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36503 5 36578
Reset O 0 36542 10 36578
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36579
Name     &xThe Shadowed Cleft&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     A small, dark tunnel hidden behind a large rock formation. 
Infernal sentries stand motionless in the dark, their green 
flames lighting the cavern in a sickly glow.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36553
Desc      The bridge approach.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36507 5 36579
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36580
Name     &xSlag Pit Overflow A&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A quiet section of the basin floor, filled with discarded 
mining carts and piles of low-quality iron ore.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The basin floor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 36526 10 36580
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36581
Name     &xSlag Pit Overflow B&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A rocky ledge overlooking the slave quarters, frequently 
patrolled by Dark Iron slavers.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The basin floor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36501 5 36581
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36582
Name     &xAshlands Overflow A&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A flat expanse of grey ash, where several buzzards are 
fighting over the remains of a slagspider.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    36552
Desc      The ashlands.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36504 5 36582
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36583
Name     &xAshlands Overflow B&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A jagged field of obsidian shards that makes travel 
slow and dangerous.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36552
Desc      The ashlands.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36514 10 36583
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36584
Name     &xThe Deep Fissure&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A massive crack in the earth near the base of the mountain. 
From here, you can see the glowing forms of molten giants 
