~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36553
Desc      The bridge approach.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36511 1 36584
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36585
Name     &xThorium Point Overflow A&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A small storage shed containing spools of silk and 
