~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36565
Desc      The plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36508 5 36586
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36587
Name     &yFiregut Overflow A&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A side tunnel in the ogre caves where several large 
