#ROOM
Vnum     36589
Name     &xThe Burning Slag&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A section of the basin where the slag is particularly fresh 
and hot, sparking with elemental energy.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    36569
Desc      The basin floor.~
#ENDEXIT
