#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36591
Name     &rMountain Landing - West&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high, stone balcony overlooking the lava canyon to the west. 
Flamewaker scouts slither through the shadows here.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    36561
Desc      The spire landing.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 36520 1 36591
#ENDROOM

