#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     36594
Name     &xThe Obsidian Grotto&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     A natural cave filled with sharp obsidian formations. 
Glassweb spiders have spun nearly invisible webs here.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    36577
